  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. All 13 credibility factors are fully assessed with achievedLevel meeting or exceeding requiredLevel. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification and sensitivity analysis on hemolysis predictions are documented. Decision: Accepted.",
